Direct Known Subclasses:
AgentMBeanManager, LoaderMBeanManager, TextIndexMBeanManager, WXSMapMBeanManager
public abstract class MBeanGroupManager<M>
extends java.lang.Object

This is an abstract base class to create a SummaryMBean for a collection of homogenous MBeans. It has two methods to retrieve a TabularData of EVERY attribute of all the mbeans as well as one with only the attributes for an external monitor. Typically, the monitor only attributes exclude things like calculated statistics which a 'real' JMX monitor will calculate it self.
